PURPOSE:-
--------
To verify the split horizon mechanism.


SCENARIO:-
---------

1-----2-----3------4-----5------6--X---7-----8
                                |            |
                                |            |
                                9            |
                                |            |
                                |            |
                                10----------11

CBR is used to send 500 data segments, each of 512 bytes, from
node 1 to node 8.

Link between 6 and 7 fails.


RUN:-
----
Type '<QUALNET_HOME>/bin/qualnet default.config'.


DESCRIPTION OF THE FILES:-
-------------------------
1. default.app -  QualNet configuration file for application input.
2. default.config - QualNet configuration input file.
3. default.expected.stat - QualNet statistics collection.
4. default.fault - QualNet configuration file for fault.
5. README - This file.
